<section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-9a39a77 elementor-section-content-middle elementor-section-height-min-height elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-items-middle" data-e-type="section" data-element_type="section" data-id="9a39a77" data-settings='{"background_background":"classic"}'><div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no"><div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-15552466" data-e-type="column" data-element_type="column" data-id="15552466"><div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-9db5168 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-e-type="widget" data-element_type="widget" data-id="9db5168" data-widget_type="heading.default"><h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">BIO</h3></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-aafb4e7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-e-type="widget" data-element_type="widget" data-id="aafb4e7" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><p class="p1"><span class="s2">Hello, I'm Elizabeth Arnau.</span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">Creativity has always been at the heart of everything I do — I've been drawing and designing since I was a little girl.</span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">In 2005, I turned that passion into a career as a fashion illustrator and designer, showing collections in Barcelona, China, New York and Cannes, before naturally evolving into an international career in modeling and acting.</span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">Today, my artistic vision extends behind the camera, where I lead the creative direction of fashion, beauty and lifestyle campaigns, and create photography and videography content for leading brands, while continuing to design original fashion illustrations.</span></p></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-1ea5710 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-e-type="widget" data-element_type="widget" data-id="1ea5710" data-widget_type="heading.default"><h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default"><span data-elementor-setting-key="title" data-pen-placeholder="Teclea aquí..." style="font-style: normal;clear: both">EXHIBITIONS &amp; AWARDS</span></h3></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e2a667a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-e-type="widget" data-element_type="widget" data-id="e2a667a" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><p style="font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"> </span></p><p style="font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">Art Exhibition of Elizabeth Arnau Artwork at <span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">Wework</span></span> Glòries, Barcelona – 30/01/2020.</span></p><p style="font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">Awarded with the <span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">Golden Thimble </span></span>at<span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;"> </span></span>Westin Palace Hotel, Madrid – 24/07/2015.</span></p><p style="font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">Elizabeth Arnau Haute Couture <strong>Fashion Show at L’Illa Diagonal</strong> in cooperation with Zapata Jewelry – 20/06/2013.</span></p><p style="font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">Art Exhibition </span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-style: normal;">of Elizabeth Arnau Artwork</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-style: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 16px;">at </span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">Miró Museum </span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;">in a private Gala organized by Hello Kitty</span><span style="font-size: 16px;">, Barcelona – 7/10/2011.</span></p><p style="font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">Charity Fashion Show in <span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">collaboration with Hello Kitty</span></span> for relief the victims of Tsunami in Japan at Elephant Barcelona – 08/04/2011.</span></p><p style="font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">Elizabeth Arnau Haute Couture &amp; Prêt-à-porter Fashion Show at <span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">Cannes Fashion Week in</span></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;"> Villa Oxygene – </span></span>2011.</span></p><p style="font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">Elizabeth Arnau Haute Couture Fashion Show at <span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">New York Couture Fashion Week</span></span>, Waldorf Astoria Hotel, NYC – 10/09/2010.</span></p><p style="font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">Elizabeth Arnau Prêt-à-porter collection at</span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;"> China Fashion Week</span></span> – CIGF 2009 International Garment &amp; Textile Fair – 10/20/2009.</span></p><p style="font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"> </span></p></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ed8dbf0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-e-type="widget" data-element_type="widget" data-id="ed8dbf0" data-widget_type="heading.default"><h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">PRESS</h3></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-0ae2a9f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-e-type="widget" data-element_type="widget" data-id="0ae2a9f" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><p style="line-height: 15.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt 0cm;">Elizabeth Arnau has been published in several press such as: Robb Report, Hola.com, Vanidad, FHM, The Bay Fashion, RB Fashion, Elegant and Dreamingless.</p></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a7692c0 elementor-arrows-position-inside elementor-widget elementor-widget-image-carousel" data-e-type="widget" data-element_type="widget" data-id="a7692c0" data-settings='{"navigation":"arrows","autoplay_speed":4000,"speed":400,"image_spacing_custom":{"unit":"px","size":1,"sizes":[]},"slides_to_show":"2","slides_to_scroll":"2","autoplay":"yes","pause_on_hover":"yes","pause_on_interaction":"yes","infinite":"yes","image_spacing_custom_tablet":{"unit":"px","size":"","sizes":[]},"image_spacing_custom_mobile":{"unit":"px","size":"","sizes":[]}}' data-widget_type="image-carousel.default"><div aria-label="Carrusel de imágenes" aria-roledescription="carousel" class="elementor-image-carousel-wrapper swiper" dir="ltr" role="region"><div aria-live="off" class="elementor-image-carousel swiper-wrapper"><div aria-label="1 de 28" aria-roledescription="slide" class="swiper-slide" role="group"><figure class="swiper-slide-inner"><noscript><img alt="Press_05" class="swiper-slide-image" decoding="async" src="/assets/images/elementor/thumbs/Press_05-oopa4kjwwg40lmfv8ops11ksts6uvrcdkn6ea2jqgo.jpg"/></noscript><img loading="lazy" src="/assets/images/elementor/thumbs/Press_05-oopa4kjwwg40lmfv8ops11ksts6uvrcdkn6ea2jqgo.jpg" alt="Press_05" class="swiper-slide-image" decoding="async"/></figure></div><div aria-label="2 de 28" aria-roledescription="slide" class="swiper-slide" role="group"><figure class="swiper-slide-inner"><noscript><img alt="Press_24" class="swiper-slide-image" decoding="async" src="/assets/images